build with: dpkg-buildpackage -us -uc
for arch, from inside imgconv-arch: makepkg -si (in an arch environment)

flatpak (inside the flatpak folder):
Build: flatpak-builder --force-clean --repo=repo-dir build-dir com.example.ImgConv.json
Bundle: flatpak build-bundle repo-dir imgconv.flatpak com.example.ImgConv

